Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/DevanR/dotvim.git ~/.vim

	install vim-plug

	:PlugInstall

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory:

    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

Upgrading all bundled plugins

    :PlugUpdate

Notes
    https://github.com/junegunn/vim-plug
    Install Markdown (http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/)
    Install ctags
    On OSX: Run git config --global core.editor /usr/bin/vim
            Install Solarized palettes for Terminal and iTerm2
